      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 475: 🟡 Suggestions - The new plugin transform path runs synchronously inside the commit-processing callback. If a plugin transform is slow or performs I/O, it can block conversation update handling and delay member/status processing. Consider dispatching `transformSwarmMessages()` to the same asynchronous/plugin worker path used for other plugin processing, then calling `updateMessageBodyOverwrite()` when the result is available. This keeps the conversation ingestion path responsive.",
